Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/7ce8dafa-b6d1-4419-83d1-a4da50a3438a) for commit 43748509a73e7936cde2b8ea8b36134664cd3a07.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/c2fe6662-3b97-4372-a52b-07bc4bdadb06/to/7ce8dafa-b6d1-4419-83d1-a4da50a3438a) against commit 5a2e66e19981cc4b79c2c15aa7916470b6a4d483:
```diff
  Benchmark                                           Metric         Change
  =========================================================================
- ~Mathlib.Algebra.Module.PID                         instructions     3.8%
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.LocallyConvex.WithSeminorms       instructions   -17.3%
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.Seminorm                          instructions    -7.4%
+ ~Mathlib.FieldTheory.RatFunc                        instructions    -2.5%
- ~Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.Trace                        instructions    12.6%
+ ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.FiniteMeasure        instructions   -13.3%
+ ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.ProbabilityMeasure   instructions   -20.1%
```
